</style>

<div class="aap-contact-v1">
  <section class="aap-section">
    <div class="aap-wrap aap-grid-2">
      <div>
        <span class="aap-kicker">Contact AdvanceAPractice</span>
        <h1>Talk through your current bottlenecks, systems, and growth priorities.</h1>
        <p>AdvanceAPractice works with healthcare practices that need cleaner workflow, stronger billing follow-through, more organized credentialing, more practical documentation support, and a calmer operational model behind growth.</p>
        <p>If your practice is dealing with administrative overload, denial-heavy billing, provider onboarding delays, after-hours charting, or systems that are technically in place but not working well enough, this is the right place to start the conversation.</p>
        <p>Portland-rooted and serving practices across Oregon, Washington, and throughout the U.S., AdvanceAPractice is built for implementation-focused support, not vague recommendations and not generic vendor language.</p>

        <div class="aap-actions">
          <a class="aap-btn primary" href="mailto:info@advanceapractice.com">Email AdvanceAPractice</a>
          <a class="aap-btn secondary" href="/resources/">Explore Resources</a>
        </div>

        <div class="aap-proof">
          <div class="aap-proof-card">
            <strong>Practical first conversation</strong>
            <span>The goal is to identify what is actually slowing the practice down, not push a canned package.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="aap-proof-card">
            <strong>Current-system aware</strong>
            <span>The approach is designed to improve current workflows where workable instead of forcing unnecessary replacement.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="aap-proof-card">
            <strong>Built for implementation</strong>
            <span>Support is structured around follow-through, adoption, workflow clarity, and real operational use.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="aap-form-card">
        <h3>Start with the issue that is creating the most drag.</h3>
        <p>This intake is designed to route the right conversation faster and keep the next step clear.</p>

        <form action="/wp-admin/admin-post.php" method="post" accept-charset="UTF-8">
          <input type="hidden" name="action" value="aap_capture_lead">
          <input type="hidden" name="form_name" value="Contact Page Lead Form">
          <input type="hidden" name="service_context" value="Contact Page Inquiry">
          <input type="hidden" name="page_title" value="Contact">

          <div class="aap-form-grid">
            <div>
              <label for="aap-practice-name">Practice name</label>
              <input id="aap-practice-name" name="practice_name" type="text" required>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="aap-role">Decision-maker role</label>
              <input id="aap-role" name="decision_maker_role" type="text" placeholder="Owner, administrator, operations leader">
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="aap-name">Decision-maker name</label>
              <input id="aap-name" name="decision_maker_name" type="text" required>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="aap-email">Email</label>
              <input id="aap-email" name="email" type="email" required>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="aap-specialty">Specialty</label>
              <input id="aap-specialty" name="specialty" type="text" placeholder="Therapy, psychiatry, PMHNP, outpatient medical">
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="aap-providers">Number of providers</label>
              <input id="aap-providers" name="provider_count" type="text">
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="aap-states">States served</label>
              <input id="aap-states" name="states_served" type="text">
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="aap-ehr">Current EHR / PM system</label>
              <input id="aap-ehr" name="ehr_pm_system" type="text" placeholder="SimplePractice, TherapyNotes, athenahealth, Tebra">
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="aap-service">Primary service interest</label>
              <select id="aap-service" name="service_interest" required>
                <option value="">Select one</option>
                <option>Mental Health Billing Services</option>
                <option>Medical Billing Services</option>
                <option>Provider Credentialing Services</option>
                <option>AI Documentation</option>
                <option>AI Revenue Cycle Support</option>
                <option>Practice Automation Consulting</option>
              </select>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="aap-timeline">Desired timeline</label>
              <select id="aap-timeline" name="desired_timeline">
                <option value="">Select one</option>
                <option>As soon as possible</option>
                <option>Within 30 days</option>
                <option>Within 60-90 days</option>
                <option>Exploring options</option>
              </select>
            </div>

            <div class="aap-full">
              <label for="aap-bottleneck">Current top bottleneck</label>
              <textarea id="aap-bottleneck" name="slowdown" required placeholder="Tell us what is slowing the practice down right now."></textarea>
            </div>

            <div class="aap-full">
              <label for="aap-goal">What would you like to improve in the next 90 days?</label>
              <textarea id="aap-goal" name="goal_90_day"></textarea>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="aap-actions">
            <button class="aap-btn primary" type="submit">Start the Conversation</button>
          </div>

          <p class="aap-note">Prefer a direct email first? Contact <a href="mailto:info@advanceapractice.com">info@advanceapractice.com</a>. Do not include patient PHI in your initial message.</p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="aap-section aap-sea">
    <div class="aap-wrap aap-grid-3">
      <div class="aap-card">
        <h3>Email first</h3>
        <p><a href="mailto:info@advanceapractice.com">info@advanceapractice.com</a></p>
        <p>Email is the cleanest first step for most inquiries and helps keep the intake organized.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="aap-card">
        <h3>Geography</h3>
        <p>Portland-rooted, serving practices across Oregon, Washington, and throughout the U.S.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="aap-card">
        <h3>Support model</h3>
        <p>Remote-first, with in-person support available where appropriate and workable.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="aap-section aap-sand">
    <div class="aap-wrap aap-grid-2">
      <div>
        <span class="aap-kicker">What Happens Next</span>
        <h2>A cleaner process than the typical contact page.</h2>
        <p>Once you submit the form, the next step is a more focused review of the current bottlenecks, systems, service priorities, and operational reality of the practice. The goal is to determine where the best starting point is, not force every practice into the same conversation.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Review the current bottlenecks and service fit</li>
          <li>Clarify systems, workflow pressure points, and timing</li>
          <li>Identify the most useful next step for the practice</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="aap-panel">
        <div class="aap-panel-inner">
          <h3>Best fit for this page</h3>
          <p>Practice owners, administrators, founders, operations leaders, and healthcare teams that know they need better workflow, stronger billing follow-through, more organized credentialing, or more practical AI implementation support.</p>
          <p><a href="/mental-health-billing/">Mental Health Billing</a><br>
          <a href="/ai-revenue-cycle/">AI Billing</a><br>
          <a href="/credentialing-accelerator/">Credentialing</a><br>
          <a href="/practice-automation-consulting/">Consulting</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
